Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《指定幸存者》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on "Designated Survivor"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几块子弹碎片残留在你的胸腔里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Several bullet fragments lodged in your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要尽快动手术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to operate as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  你现在是美国代理总统了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you're now the acting president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到枪手了  他们在指挥中心等你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They found the shooter. They're waiting for you at Command Ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼总统会想要生擒他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Kirkman would have wanted to take him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不对  下达命令吧  就地射杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a mistake. Give the order. Shoot to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处决疑犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Execute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标已歼灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Target neutralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚特伍德先生  只要你照我说的去做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Atwood, your son will be safe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的儿子就会没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as long as you do - everything I tell you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜·威尔士  他们抓到的是她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah Wells? That's who they have in custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.27,0:00:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄清楚她到底知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find out what she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果总统想要答案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the President wants answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只会告诉一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll give them to one person --
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统本人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the President himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clear the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想告诉我一些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand you have some things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于彼得·麦克利什的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you want to tell me about Peter MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什当时藏在防爆掩体里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}MacLeish was hiding in a bomb shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在爆炸之前就藏进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Moments before the explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在播放途中有一个34秒的间隙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there was a 34-second gap in the broadcast feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:00:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他准确地知道何时该离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knew exactly when to leave his seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从最开始就牵涉此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was involved from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禽兽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪射击他的人  麦克利什也认识他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man who shot him -- MacLeish knew him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  他们一起在阿富汗服过役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. They served together in Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.91,0:01:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前中情局特工内斯特·洛萨诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Former CIA operative Nestor Lozano,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代号"卡特兰"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}code name "Catalan."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}中央情报报告\N内斯特·罗萨诺  化名卡特兰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我现在没有所有证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, I don't have all the pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在麦克利什议员当选副总统之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I did feel I had enough to go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得自己证据足够去告诉霍斯拉滕议员了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to Speaker Hookstraten before MacLeish was confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  你这么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Damn right you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What exactly happened there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在去听证会的路上  我遇到了袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was attacked on the way to the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在去楼雷本大厦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was on my way to meet Speaker Hookstraten
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见霍斯拉滕议员的路上遇袭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at the Rayburn Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某人撞了我车的中部  想将我掐死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone T-boned my car, tried to strangle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我逃走了  但他拿走了我的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got away, but he took my file.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的是  里特特工能够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Luckily, Agent Ritter was able to secure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全地从局里拿到另一份副本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}another copy from the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真蠢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I feel so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什愚弄了所有人  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}MacLeish fooled everyone, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了她  她看透了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not her. She saw right through him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-赛斯  我以为你在医院呢  -刚回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Seth, I thought you'd be at the hospital. - Just got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么样  恢复得快吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is he? Recovering rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统应该在这周结束之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President should be back in the residence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-回到白宫  -好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- by the end of the week. - Great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到消息  我们注意到...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaking of news, sir, we noticed your team --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的团队今天晚些时候安排了一场新闻发布会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}uh, that your team scheduled a press conference for later today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为需要使公众安心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I-I think the people need reassurance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国仍然在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that their country remains in capable hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯特曼总统的统领之下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with President Kirkman in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的情操真是让人钦佩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an admirable sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  我对这个时机很好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just, uh, curious about the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许您能让我们看看您的发言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we could take a look at your remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都搞定了  谢谢  赛斯  谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's handled. Thank you, Seth. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.31,0:02:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  麦克利什在与艾尔萨卡合作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, MacLeish was working with Al-Sakar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔萨卡不是爆炸事件的罪魁祸首\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Al-Sakar isn't behind the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我在审问马吉德·纳萨尔时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I interviewed Majid Nassar,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他之所以承认负责此次袭击事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he told me that he took responsibility for the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了让真正的凶手脱离我们的视线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in order to divert us from the real conspirators.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是艾尔萨卡的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if it wasn't Al-Sakar --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什也不可能一个人完成这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, MacLeish couldn't have done this on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谁是他的同伙  -我们还不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Who is he working with? - We don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查尔斯·兰登脱不了关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charles Langdon is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里士满总统的幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Richmond's Chief of Staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为他在爆炸中牺牲了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought he died in the bombing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以亲自作证  他在爆炸中存活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can personally verify that he survived the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:02:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾亲眼见过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  他正藏匿在某个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, he's hiding out in some --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员  这是我妻子  艾丽克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells, this is my wife, Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很高兴见到你  -夫人您好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Pleased to meet you. - Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请继续\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请恕我直言  总统先生  此消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Respectfully, sir, this information
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能向您和您的安保团队透露\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is only for you and your security team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员  我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells, I promise you --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.78,0:03:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用  没关系的  汤姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, it's okay, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我过会儿再来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll -- I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以向你保证  没有这个必要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assure you that wasn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-麦克  请  -对不起  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mike, please -- - I'm sorry, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不得不赞同威尔士探员的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I have to agree with Agent Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一夫人不在您的安保团队内\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The First Lady isn't a part of your security team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没有保密权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't have code-word clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她对这个威胁评估是知情的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She knows about the threat assessment --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是个错误  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that was a mistake, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时可没这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You didn't say that at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm saying it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我们现在面临的是一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, we're dealing with a conspiracy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极其危险叵测的阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's so deep, so dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以至于没有人是安全的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that nobody's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时  向外部人员透露信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And not only is sharing information
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅会对国家安全造成威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with outside personnel a threat to national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也会使您信任的人处于危险之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It also puts the people you confide in at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  您必须缩小亲信的范围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you need to tighten your circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在该做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让麦克利什尽快落网\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want MacLeish in custody as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常来说  我会建议咨询总检察长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ordinarily, I'd say we consult with the Attorney General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们现在没有总检察长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we don't have an Attorney General.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们可以相信谁  我能联系他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know someone we can trust. Can I reach out to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以给你提供一间办公室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've got an office you could use.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你从秘密通道自由进出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can get you in and out through covert access
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时维持对外你仍处于拘留之中的说辞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and maintain your cover story you're still in police custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你得秘密行动  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You need to stay in the shadows. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你再回来时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to come back to me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一个捉拿麦克利什的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with a plan on how to get MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋会付出代价的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The son of a bitch is gonna pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能阻止他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副总统有权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president has the authority
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安排他自己的新闻发布会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to schedule his own press conferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什的新闻发布会是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, what's this about a MacLeish press conference?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副总统有权安排自己的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The vice president has the authority to schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-新闻发  -这我理解  但为什么是现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- his own press -- - I understand that, but why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这问题你得问麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd have to take that up with MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'd like to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总统给我交待了行动项目清单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I have a laundry list of action items from POTUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你什么时候跟他说过话的  -一小时前吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When did you speak to him? - About an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没告诉我你为什么要调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, no, he didn't say why you were looking into
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我两年半前打的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the phone calls I made 2 1/2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说  我觉得现在不适合问这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And, frankly, I didn't think it was the right time to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有情况及时通知我  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep me posted, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么是我不知道的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Am I missing something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要说吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是前检察官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because you're a former U.S. Attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你具备刚正不阿的品格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a man of absolute integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而如今  总统需要一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And right now, the president needs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可指责的法律顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a legal advisor who's above reproach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的有些超出我的职责范围了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you're asking is just a little above my pay grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这超过了所有人的职责范围\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's above all of our pay grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事是史无前例的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we're talking about is completely unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总统需要顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the president needs counsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经告诉他我们可以指望你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I might have already told him that we can count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  可以吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So...can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么一番甜言蜜语  我怎么能拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, when you sweet-talk a guy like that, how can I refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在过去的几周里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Through these past weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯克曼总统证明了他是我们可以信赖的领导人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}President Kirkman has shown himself to be a leader we can trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具有良好品德和能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a leader who has the virtue and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使国家团结一致  我对他的归来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to keep this nation united, and I couldn't be more thrilled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示兴奋不已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be welcoming him back to the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺杀总统未遂与国会爆炸案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The assassination attempt and the Capitol bombing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是针对我们民主共和国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were attacks on the very foundations
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根基的攻击  但他们都失败了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of this democratic republic, and they failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你知道这件事吗  -他们也永远不会成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Did you know about this? - ...just as they will always fail...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-赛斯提醒过我  -...一次又一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Seth gave me a heads-up. - ...time and time again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可真是有胆量啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. He's got some nerve going out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就这么独自上阵  -不仅因为我们强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- on his own like that. - ...not only because we're strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还因为我们团结一心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but because we are united,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秉持着共同价值观与希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}woven together through common values and hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此  我想感谢勇敢的执法部门官员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to thank the brave law-enforcement officers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who brought the --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得回白宫了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to go back to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很快就能出院了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, you'll be out of here soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我是说现在  我不能在这干坐着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I mean now. I can't just sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  你刚受到枪击  能活下来已是万幸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, you just got shot. You are lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽克斯  这一切的幕后主使依然逍遥法外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, the people that are behind this are still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白宫里出了个叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a traitor in the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干等在这里是抓不到他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am not gonna find them by just sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  汤姆  我得跟你说件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}O-Okay, Tom, I need to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你中枪前不久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Minutes before you got shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽发现是当初\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily found out that it was Aaron
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚伦打电话给五角大楼的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who made that call to the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽为什么要告诉你这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why the hell is Emily talking to you about stuff like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么不来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why didn't she come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们第一次有机会谈这事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the first opportunity that we've had.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And with regards to Aaron,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是有什么解释的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there has to be some kind of explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, any number of people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都有可能让他打这通电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}could have asked him to make that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但我们得考虑的确是他的可能性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, but we have to consider the possibility that it is him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那我会跟他谈  用证据跟他对质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine, then I'll talk to him, confront him with the evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他能自我辩驳  -不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- and he can explain himself. - You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  你自己之前都说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, you yourself said just the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能相信任何人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we can't trust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着艾伦奋死拼搏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I watched Aaron fight tooth and nail
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来保卫和守护我的总统之位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to protect and secure my presidency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果艾伦与恐怖分子有关  如果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Aaron is involved with the terrorist -- if --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你面对他  对他摊牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you confront him and you show him your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是把自己推向更危险的境地中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're putting yourself at even more risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是我在查清楚之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not exactly like I can freeze him out
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把他排除在外  我需要他的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until I get to the bottom of this. I need his help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定有办法能在不引起怀疑的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there has to be a way to keep him at arm's length
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疏远他的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without arousing suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太不可思议了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  动用的资源和企划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, the resources involved and the planning...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一场副总统参与的阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a conspiracy that reaches all the way to the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉我怀疑你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I doubted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是局里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just the bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个国家都亏欠了你许多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The whole country owes you a great debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是  这些证据还不够充足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unfortunately, this isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.59,0:08:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道麦克利什有罪是一回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's one thing to know that MacLeish is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定罪是另一回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's another one to nail him for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还需要什么  我有照片  我有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What more do we need? I have the photos. I have the...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的可是指控美国的副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're talking about accusing the vice president of the United States
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参与了史上最严重的犯罪之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of being involved in one of the greatest crimes in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要能将他和阴谋联系起来的直接证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need direct evidence tying him to the conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们甚至都没有足够的证据拘留他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't even have enough to detain him,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更别说让他害怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}much less make him sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们去找实证  找人对他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then we find grounds. We -- We get someone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,施施压力  逼他坦白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to -- to apply the heat, and we flush him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪手是我们最大的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The gunman was our best bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什有其他的同伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}MacLeish has other partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  我以为你说你没有关于她的线索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. I thought you said you didn't have a lead on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是没有  但是杰森·亚特伍德也许有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't. But Jason Atwood might.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hannah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们单独说说话  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave us now. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他们把监控关了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had them turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有耳目  只有你我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No eyes, no ears, just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.03,0:09:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗  发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How -- How are you? What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's nothing. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.74,0:09:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人怎么样了  卢克怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's my family? How's Luke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没人跟你说吗  -说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nobody told you? - Tell me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在单独监禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been in solitary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森  还是没找到卢克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason, Luke is still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  这跟说好的不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that wasn't the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-杰森  听我说  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Jason, listen to me. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把关于麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told the president everything about MacLeish,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特兰  还有蓝图的一切告诉了总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catalan, the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你毋须保护任何东西了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is nothing left for you to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你对她了解多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me what you know about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片哪里来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我拍的  -还记得你留给我的线索吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I took it. - You gave me the lead, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威德尔案  我知道他们带走了卢克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Weddle case. I knew they had Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道了他们正是借此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also knew this is how they got you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要挟你承认谋杀纳萨尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to confess to Nassar's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森  撤回你的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason, take your statement back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你知道的一切都告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell me everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  如果他们知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to me -- if they know
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我在和你合作...  -不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- that I'm cooperating with you... - They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纳萨尔被关在最高设防的联邦监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They had Nassar in a federal maximum-security prison
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们却仍能杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and still got to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们已经暴露了  我们识穿了麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're exposed now. We know about MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-杰森  -汉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Jason... - Hannah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.88,0:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  我们需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. We need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想帮我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就找回我儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}find my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道的是  根据白宫总机接线员的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I know is what the White House switchboard operator told me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会大厦的威胁评估报告\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Aaron made the call to the Secretary of Defense
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被五角大楼撤回前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}right before the threat-assessment memo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是亚伦给国防部长打了电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was recalled by the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他与你对质了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he confronted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  他知道了我在打听事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. He found out I was making inquiries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很生气  并且询问我在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was very upset. He asked what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉他  他得来问您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told him he needed to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  很抱歉我将你置于如此境地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, I'm -- I'm sorry I put you in this position,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后的事就交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'll handle it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定不需要我跟进吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you sure you don't want me to follow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我可以...  -不用了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I can... - No, I've got it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.35,0:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间的谈话不能让别人知道  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to keep this conversation between us. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好的  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of course. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  你不会真觉得他是叛徒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, you don't really think he's a traitor, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不这么觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我有十足把握前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But until I can prove that definitively,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得保持警惕  你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to keep my guard up, and so do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今时不同往日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're living in a different world today than we were yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么了  -霍斯拉滕议长来了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah? - Speaker Hookstraten is here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  让她进来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, send her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你能在这么短的时间内与我会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for seeing me on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  议长女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, of course, Madam Speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如之前所说  我只能给你几分钟的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, as I said before, I can only give you a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.07,0:12:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半分钟就好  我要见总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This will take 30 seconds. I need to see the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,议长女士...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ma'am --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果并非要事  我也不会提出请求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't be asking if it wasn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解  但总统先生仍在康复中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand, but the president's still in recovery right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很显然  他仍在工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clearly, he's still conducting business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要与他会面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So... I need to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如告诉我是什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why don't you tell me what it's regarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会转告他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll relay it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这完全是总统先生与我之间的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What this is regarding is strictly between me and the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言  议长女士  我是总统的幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Respectfully, Madam Speaker, I-I'm his Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解事态是我的职责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's my job to know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是的  但我不会告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps, but not from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会知道是什么事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll know what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他想  可以告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He can tell you if he wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不会背叛他的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm not gonna betray his confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力帮你安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll try and schedule you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,务必尽力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能帮忙找到卢克·亚特伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can help find Luke Atwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让我联系州警  -别把这事私人化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Let me liaise with state police -- - Don't make this personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是私事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我向杰森保证了会尽一切努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promised Jason I would do everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  那个男孩从被绑架开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, and the boy has been a state-wide
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就已经成了全州范围内的首要任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}priority since he was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚看到我又增派了三名探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You just saw me put - three more agents on it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们中任何一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, each one of them is more qualified
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在失踪人口上都比你更有资历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in missing persons than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在的任务是为总统制定计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your job right now is to come up with a plan for the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在不能有个人感情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't afford to have feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己也知道我说的是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm right. And you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now let's get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  请容我再表达一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, let me say again
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝丝和我知道你安然无恙有多么的高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how relieved Beth and I are to know you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对我意义重大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That means a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到我早上的评论了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You catch my remarks this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我很欣赏  非常感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I did, and I - appreciated them. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于昨晚  你可能听说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In regards to last night, you may have heard
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些内部意见分歧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that there was some internal disagreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下达了杀无赦的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gave the shoot-to-kill order
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想看到更多无辜的人受到伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause I didn't want to see more innocent people get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有情报都显示此人是专业杀手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the intel suggested this guy was a pro,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不会接受被活捉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he wasn't gonna be taken alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能处理方式不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might have handled it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果说成为总统之后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if there's one thing that I've learned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我学到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since becoming president,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是做在极大的压力下生死抉择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's how difficult it is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多么的艰难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make life-and-death decisions under extreme pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仅承担了这份工作一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I only held the job for a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就已经让我感激\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it did make me appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为国家所做的一切了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everything you've done for this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then what did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他向我表示感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He thanked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后告诉我他希望我接手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then he told me he wants me to take over
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本月余下的公开日程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}his public schedule for the rest of the month,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到他完全康复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}till he's back at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, that's excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就是你要做的  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's what you'll do. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时  我们静待进一步指示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And for the moment, we lay low until further instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪种指示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一次刺杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Another attempt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在短期内我们会巩固现有成果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we consolidate our gains in the short term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝丝  还有太多未了结的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beth, there are so many loose ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人去处理未了结的事了  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the loose ends are being attended to, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡特兰已经死了  威尔士探员被监禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Catalan is dead. Agent Wells is in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会被解决掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'll be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会平安度过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一向如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没有这么生气过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never felt anger like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这辈子还从没打过人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I've never even hit someone in my entire life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上小学时都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not even in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是那个和事佬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was always the peacemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我看到他时  他就站在那儿笑着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when I saw him... just standing there, smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想伸手掐死他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to reach out and strangle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我觉得我本可能杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Honestly, I think I could have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你藏得很好  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hid it well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他以为他是在耍你  但事实上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He thinks he's playing you, but in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在大家眼中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's a prisoner in plain sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美国公众一致认为的囚犯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in full view of the American public,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更别提还有一群特工处的特工\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not to mention a phalanx of Secret Service agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要耐心等待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We just got to be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就会出纰漏  放松警惕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'll make a mistake, lower his guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when he does...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.19,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就任我处置了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您感觉怎么样  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you feeling, Mr. President?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多了  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Much better. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  你想从哪儿开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. Where would you like to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你跟艾米丽关系紧张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand there's some tension between you and Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直在查我的通话记录\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's been looking into my phone records.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我让她查的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At my direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要求她不要让你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also asked her to keep you out of the loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能问为什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}May I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我该给你个解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. You... You deserve an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是我的参谋长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're my Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实是  在特工处的要求下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is, at the request of the Secret Service,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不重新审查我的整个核心交际圈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have had to re-vet my entire inner circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那场爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because of the bombing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当晚有上千人丧生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a thousand people died that night, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.32,0:16:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且事件疑云重重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it left more questions than answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-希望你能理解  -当然  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I hope you understand. - Yeah. Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让艾米丽负责你的背景调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I asked Emily to coordinate your background check.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她自然不能泄露这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So naturally, she couldn't divulge what she was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是机密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because it was classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉给你带来了困扰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I apologize for any confusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但责任在我  不在艾米丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it was my call, not Emily's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  您没必要道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, there's no need for apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都说得通了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It all makes perfect sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  很好  你有什么消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Great. What have you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍斯拉滕议长来见我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaker Hookstraten came to see me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说她要跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she said she needed to talk to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说你知道是什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you would know what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有隐情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们穷追不舍  他定会露出马脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We shake this tree hard enough, it'll fall out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什部队的八名幸存者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The eight surviving members of MacLeish's army unit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年来一直在说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have all been lying for a decade.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们之间肯定有突破口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's got to be a weak link in here somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有人有个人问题  吸毒  酗酒之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}someone with personal problems, drugs, booze, something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你是怎么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找出那个人并从他突破  但要小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We find that person... and break him, but carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能让让麦克利什察觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't afford to tip MacLeish off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是想引蛇出洞  而不是打草惊蛇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to rattle his cage, not shatter it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  救命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉  我不是故意要吓你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你还好吗  爸爸  -我还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you okay, Daddy? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了个噩梦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手上的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you got there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你画了幅画\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I drew it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是从博物馆偷来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you steal it from a museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是我画的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I drew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸刚才大叫了一声  -他没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Daddy screamed. - He did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你站在这里多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How -- how long have you been standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直等到欣赏完你的美妙琴声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long enough to hear how good you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道你弹得这么好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't even know you played.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经很认真地练过一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was serious about it for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在只当是一种放松方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but now I just play to release stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有效果吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚从医院回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, I just got back from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你为什么这么谨慎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, I-I get why you're being so cagey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事关国家机密\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a matter of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦  他让我审查你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron, he asked me to vet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事需严格保密  所以你问我的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was strictly classified, so when you confronted me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能向你说出详情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't tell you what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解  他告诉我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. No, he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉  我之前有点不理智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I-I was a bit of a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的  这对于我们俩都很有压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get it. It was stressful for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有什么事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you, uh -- you take any requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}摩托车维修中心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,XL1200C型赛车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}XL1200C Sportster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是辆好车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a nice ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修好后我可以给你开一个好价钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I can get you a good price on her once I'm through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这车对我来说有点大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it's a little bit too much bike for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-阿尔文·乔纳  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Alvin Joyner? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局探员  约翰逊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Special Agent Johnson, FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我几周前和联调局的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already talked to the FBI, weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈过麦克利什队长的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about Captain MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个例行的背景后续调查而已  阿尔文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's just a routine follow-up on our background check, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.57,0:21:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局里不希望出任何差错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Bureau doesn't like to get anything wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是涉及到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially when it involves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国副总统时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the vice president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在文件正式归档之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I need to cross a few T's and dot a few I's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要确认一些信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before we can officially close the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-可以吗  -当然没问题  问吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that okay? - Yeah, sure. Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2005年11月14日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About this mission to Kunar Province,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:31.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库纳尔省的行动中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}November 14, 2005,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的事后报告说你是和20个人一起出发的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}your after-action report says you set out with 20 men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.57,0:21:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这属实吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  三支中队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Three squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们并非满员状态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we weren't full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫罗膝盖受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Morrow had a bad knee,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗德里格斯当时在休探亲假\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and Rodriguez was on family leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那为什么出勤直升机的乘客名单上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, uh, so, why does the outbound-helicopter manifest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写的是21名军人呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}say 21 troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有人弄错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe somebody made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一开始也这么认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I thought that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去问了相关技术军官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I asked the warrant officer involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说绝对没有弄错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he said absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他们绝对不会犯这样的错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said they can't afford to make mistakes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是性命攸关的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lives depend on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不知道该跟你说什么好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有可能那天有其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it possible someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你们一起行动了呢  阿尔文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}joined your mission that night, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.15,0:22:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  不可能  -你确定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. No. No way. - You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为技术军官说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because the warrant officer said that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.36,0:22:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候会派外部人员参与任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sometimes outside personnel will be assigned to missions --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报员  中情局特工之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}intelligence officers, CIA, stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  从没有过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nope. Never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们该说的都说完了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I guess we're done here then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-祝你好运  -谢谢配合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Good luck. - Thanks for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去告知总统  有好戏上演了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell the president it's game on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会去找麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gonna run to MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生  我理解您身负重担\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, I appreciate that you have a job to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但放任您在术后如此短的时间内回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I wouldn't be doing mine if I didn't advise you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.86,0:23:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我未加劝阻的话  就是我工作的失职\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}against leaving the hospital so soon after surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.41,0:23:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上校  我非常理解你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain, I understand completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我真的需要回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I really do have to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.88,0:23:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事关国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a matter of national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是你说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you were the one who said
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.37,0:23:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为我的康复速度感到高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you were really happy with my progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  但我也告诫过您不可操劳过度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}True, but I also cautioned against undue stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.51,0:23:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我恐怕是入错行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm afraid I've got the wrong job for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.06,0:23:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  你根本拗不过他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See? You're not gonna win with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也发现了  -我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So I'm discovering. - Look, I promise you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽量多休息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will do everything I can to take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且上次我查了一下  我的军衔比你高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Besides, last time I checked, I think I outrank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽克斯  我知道你生我的气了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, I know you're mad at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我真的需要回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I really do need to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're gonna have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  我注意到你看发布会时的表情了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tom, I saw the way you looked watching that press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了  与麦克利什有关吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is going on? Is it MacLeish?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能应付得来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.35,0:23:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽克斯  你没明白我的意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alex, you're not hearing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.75,0:23:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说  身为总统  你不能告诉我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean the president can't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我们不分彼此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right now, we're one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们刚从诺福克回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we're just coming back from Norfolk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还行吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it was fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地握手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shook a lot of hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在驱逐舰的舰首上开了瓶香槟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}broke a champagne bottle on a destroyer's bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些例行公事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was strictly routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.14,0:24:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美国邮政管理局
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.26,0:24:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你留下的粉笔标志了  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw your chalk mark. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:24:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乔纳  他想见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Joyner. He wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.51,0:24:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.95,0:25:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局今天来找他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The FBI came to see him today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.55,0:25:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来  为了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Again? What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.61,0:25:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是例行后续调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Said it was a routine follow-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和库纳尔任务的直升机乘客名单有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something to do with a helicopter manifest on the Kunar mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.22,0:25:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直升机乘客名单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Helicopter manifest?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.25,0:25:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我觉得只是些官僚工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. It sounds like bureaucratic busywork to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.32,0:25:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就完了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it sounds like the end of it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.57,0:25:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  但乔纳不这么想  你了解他的  队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, except for Joyner. You know Alvin, Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.94,0:25:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他比我们其余的人都要严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He took it harder than the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.38,0:25:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直进出康复中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's been in and out of rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必费多大力气就能逼死他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't take much to push him over the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.43,0:25:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想这样为难你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hate to put you in this position,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.67,0:25:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他不肯听我的  他坚持要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he wouldn't listen to me, insisted that he had to --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.16,0:25:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  我当然会见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No, no, no, no, no. Of course I'll see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.94,0:25:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.89,0:25:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.25,0:25:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即兴发挥  适时改编  完胜全场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Improvise, adapt, overcome, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.30,0:25:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell him I'll, uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.41,0:25:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在上次那个地方等他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll meet him at the, uh, same place as last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.39,0:25:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚九点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tonight, 21:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.00,0:25:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.26,0:25:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.65,0:25:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和总统说了你想见他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told the president you wanted to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.22,0:25:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-然后呢  -他说能见你时  自然会找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And? - And he said he'd get back to you when he can.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.96,0:25:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.10,0:25:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统改变了计划  议长女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president just changed his plans, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.74,0:26:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他今晚就要出院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's getting out of the hospital tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.33,0:26:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-今晚  为什么  -因为他想回来工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tonight? Why? - Because he wants to get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.61,0:26:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想和他说的事十万火急的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, listen, if what you want to share with him
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.07,0:26:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就告诉我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is time-sensitive, just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.32,0:26:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事关那位枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's about the gunman.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.74,0:26:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与他有何相关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about the gunman?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.71,0:26:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道为什么联调局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to know why the FBI
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.23,0:26:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一枪崩了我们的李·哈维·奥斯瓦尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}blew away our own Lee Harvey Oswald.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.23,0:26:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}被认为是肯尼迪总统遇刺案的主凶
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.76,0:26:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疑犯对执法机关构成了直接威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The suspect posed an immediate threat to law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.92,0:26:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少来这套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.24,0:26:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一系列空前巨大的阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a cluster of epic proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.63,0:26:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枪手是独行侠  还是某组织的成员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was the shooter a lone wolf, part of a group?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.35,0:26:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们永远不得而知了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll never know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.98,0:26:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今早麦克利什副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there was Vice President MacLeish this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.59,0:26:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却视之为一场胜仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}turning it into a victory lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.70,0:26:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-为什么  -你当时不在场  议长女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why? - You weren't in the room, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.56,0:26:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你在  亚伦  到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you were, Aaron. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.43,0:26:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什是否参与其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was MacLeish involved -- yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.54,0:26:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连总统都怀疑麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even the President has his suspicions about MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.75,0:26:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他亲口告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He told me so himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.83,0:26:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是他没告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or didn't he fill you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.43,0:26:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...  你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What -- What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.51,0:26:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他当然告诉我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course he told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.70,0:26:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你也该知道他让我盯紧麦克利什\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then you know that he asked me to keep an eye on MacLeish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.39,0:26:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要知道详情  亚伦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to be in the loop, Aaron.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.81,0:26:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我不能...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I can't --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.73,0:27:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果白宫不配合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the White House doesn't cooperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.36,0:27:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我将召开国会听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll just call a congressional hearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.77,0:27:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是记者招待会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or maybe a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.23,0:27:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能公开这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't go public with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.51,0:27:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在保护什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you trying to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.97,0:27:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是该问  你在保护谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or should I say who are you trying to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.85,0:27:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你是那个把麦克利什推上副总统之位的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After all, it was you who pushed MacLeish for V.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.36,0:27:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比其他人都积极\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.66,0:27:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说太偏颇了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now -- Now, that's low.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.99,0:27:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是事实  昨晚发生什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But accurate. What happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.35,0:27:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.15,0:27:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就在委员会上见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll see you in committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.16,0:27:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们逮到了一个枪手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had the shooter contained.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.34,0:27:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局准备活捉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}FBI was ready to apprehend,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.29,0:27:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但被麦克利什驳回了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but MacLeish overruled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.72,0:27:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.60,0:27:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他想要保护出勤特工的生命安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he wanted to protect the lives of the men on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.44,0:27:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉他总统更希望生擒抢手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told him the president would want to take him alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.14,0:27:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他还是下令了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he -- he gave the order anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:27:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么命令\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What order?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.61,0:27:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就地射杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shoot to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.47,0:28:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事不能外泄  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's for your ears only, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.22,0:28:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.69,0:28:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先开始限制他对国家安全文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We start by limiting his access
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.21,0:28:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和情报简报的读取权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to national-security documents and intelligence briefings.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.17,0:28:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会用全体工作人员安全审查做幌子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do it under the guise of a staff-wide security review.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.17,0:28:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚伦不会知道此事只针对他一人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aaron won't know he's being targeted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.56,0:28:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我希望保持他的不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, good. I want to keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.59,0:28:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还建议更新他的最高级别敏感信息权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I also recommend we renew his TS/SCI clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.47,0:28:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以获取他的经济状况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That'll give us access to his finances,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.21,0:28:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近期旅行记录和个人通讯信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}recent travel, personal contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.22,0:28:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  要记住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, just remember --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.54,0:28:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是想洗清他的嫌疑  而非毁了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we want to clear him, not bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.47,0:28:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Affirmative, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.58,0:28:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什那边怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where does that put us with MacLeish?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.32,0:28:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经设好陷阱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Trap has been set.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.66,0:28:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔士探员在监视麦克利什的一个老战友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agent Wells is sitting on one of MacLeish's old Army buddies,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.02,0:28:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等着他采取行动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just waiting for him to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.63,0:28:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时  我通知了他的安保人员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, I've filled in his security detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.86,0:28:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们按副总统要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}told them to give the vice president
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.23,0:28:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他足够的空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a wide berth, should he request it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.32,0:28:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来唯一能做的就是等待了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess the only thing left to do is wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.71,0:28:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这总是最艰难的部分  总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's always the hardest part, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.76,0:28:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.05,0:28:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在开玩笑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.92,0:28:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉过你  我们现在走每一步都要小心翼翼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you every move we make now has to be cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.40,0:29:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此暴露自己过于危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exposing yourself like this. It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.21,0:29:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前也和乔纳经历着类似的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been down this road with Joyner before.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.79,0:29:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这不...  -这不值得  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's not... - It's not worth it, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.59,0:29:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统之位唾手可得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a heartbeat away from the presidency.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.29,0:29:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让别人来善后吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let someone else fix the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.17,0:29:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是他唯一能够倾诉的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the only one he'll talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.67,0:29:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.03,0:29:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -如果他像你说得那样痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - If he's in as much pain as you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.83,0:29:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这是在帮他的忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll be doing him a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.39,0:29:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  -你不再是军人了  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. - You're not in the army anymore, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.17,0:29:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已宣誓要为更伟大的事业而奋斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We pledged ourselves to a higher cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.38,0:29:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝丝  他是我的手下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beth, he's one of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.12,0:29:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起经历过地狱般的折磨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been through hell together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.45,0:29:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在他是战争牺牲品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now he becomes another casualty of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.36,0:29:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争的牺牲品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A casualty of war?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.60,0:29:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你听到自己在说什么了吗  -你有吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Are you hearing yourself? - Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.52,0:29:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局找上他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The FBI came to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.01,0:29:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个例行的后续调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On a routine follow-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.52,0:29:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是需要打消自己的顾虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The guy just needs some reassurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.28,0:29:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能安抚好他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.62,0:29:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.42,0:30:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和他谈谈  仅此一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Talk to him this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.46,0:30:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果没用的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if it doesn't work,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.24,0:30:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就需要消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the problem has to be eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.55,0:30:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有牺牲就没有胜利  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No victory without sacrifice, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.78,0:30:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.96,0:30:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚特伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Atwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.75,0:30:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你没什么好说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got nothing to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.19,0:30:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森  事关卢克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason, it's about Luke.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.58,0:30:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jason.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.55,0:30:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.37,0:30:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-先生  -先生 \N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Sir. - Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.60,0:30:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  让他过去  让他过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No! Let him go! Let him...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.26,0:31:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车备好了  副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Car's ready, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.45,0:31:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  里奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你们两个  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just the two of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.41,0:31:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如您的要求  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As you requested, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.09,0:31:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be right down.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.21,0:31:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.01,0:31:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么喝的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got anything to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.83,0:31:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情这么"好"啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.15,0:31:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.76,0:31:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说...  好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, that -- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.60,0:32:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是瓶麦卡伦18年威士忌  你自便吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's an 18-year Macallan, but, yeah, help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.11,0:32:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.53,0:32:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为亚伦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this about Aaron?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.89,0:32:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我押20块事关"政治问题"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. I'll take - "political malaise" for $20.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.92,0:32:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还真说中了  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, you suck. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.79,0:32:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原以为自己知道这里是如何运转的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I knew how this town worked,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.17,0:32:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在我也弄不懂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it doesn't make sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.66,0:32:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一个我以为能够信赖的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, every-- everyone I thought I could count on,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.43,0:32:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每件事  都无关紧要了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}everything -- it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.53,0:32:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终都是体制获胜  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The system wins in the end, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.05,0:32:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道  也许我错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Maybe I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.20,0:32:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我太天真了  也许二者都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'm naive. Maybe I'm both.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.56,0:32:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.42,0:32:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉过你我在白宫的第一份工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did I ever tell you about how I got
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.38,0:32:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是怎么得来的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my first job at the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.11,0:32:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《哈佛讽刺文社》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harvard Lampoon connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.18,0:32:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉过你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.20,0:32:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赛斯  每次私下和你聊天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seth, nobody can have a personal conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.33,0:32:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都会提到哈佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with you without Harvard coming up,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.52,0:32:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常30秒内就会说到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}usually within the first 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.08,0:32:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是这样的  我是在剑桥上的学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not true. I always say I went to school in Cambridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.44,0:32:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  翻篇吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyway, I'm ignoring that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.82,0:32:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是  当我刚来这的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My point is that - when I first started here,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.51,0:32:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是底层员工  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I was floored, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.50,0:32:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走路不超过15米就得停下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't walk more than 50 feet without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.93,0:32:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我在这里  在白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here I was - at the White House, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.28,0:32:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二代移民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The son of immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.33,0:32:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我无法相信...  -等一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I mean, I couldn't believe -- - Wait. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.74,0:33:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我以为你父亲是一名成功的工程师  -别打岔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I thought your dad's a successful engineer. - Don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.35,0:33:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是我无法相信我能走到这步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I'm saying was that I couldn't believe that I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.82,0:33:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后工作上的烦心事就上来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then work took over,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.43,0:33:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现实开始展现出它丑陋的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and reality reared its ugly head.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.25,0:33:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才开始意识到为什么华盛顿是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I started to realize why Washington is the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.30,0:33:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来在国会大厦被袭击后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then I bump into Tom Kirkman in the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.48,0:33:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在厕所遇到了汤姆·柯克曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}after the entire government's been blown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.51,0:33:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他身上只有正直感与慈悲心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he's nothing but decency and compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.86,0:33:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为国效力的愿望远远大于自己的野心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, this guy is service over ambition,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.83,0:33:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大公无私\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}integrity above expedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.29,0:33:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是这让我感觉到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it reminded me what it felt like
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.74,0:33:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不应该只为自己着想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be part of something bigger than yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.75,0:33:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是要为我们心目中向往的美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what it felt like to be part of the kind of America
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.98,0:33:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出自己的贡献\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that you want to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.88,0:33:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚仍然是这么想的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still feel that way tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.92,0:33:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又何尝不是呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So how come I don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.06,0:33:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是完美主义者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause you're a perfectionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.59,0:33:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可突然间一切都不那么完美了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And suddenly things don't seem so perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.47,0:33:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是孩子了  赛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I'm not a child, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.56,0:33:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这世界并不完美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know things aren't perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.47,0:34:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  但你觉得自己可以让这个世界变得美好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, but you think you can make things perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.85,0:34:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.66,0:34:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是...  可能吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not that I... Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.65,0:34:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是可能吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.09,0:34:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米丽  你工作非常尽责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily, come on. You're doing a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.61,0:34:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使完美主义者也并非一帆风顺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even perfectionists have their ups and downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.81,0:34:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怪我说得简单  我觉得你只是难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not to oversimplify it, but I think you're probably sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.67,0:34:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all really sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.69,0:34:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并没有错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.77,0:34:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该回家  安全地回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need to go home, get home safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.15,0:34:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好睡一觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}get a really good night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.17,0:34:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在只有这些建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is all of my advice at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.30,0:34:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还会有更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You get more tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.38,0:34:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢  -不不不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.38,0:34:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-闭嘴吧  晚安  -晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shut up. Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.62,0:34:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有什么能帮你的吗  女士  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, ma'am, can I help you? - I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.68,0:35:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫安吉拉·琳赛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is Angela Lindsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.54,0:35:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是佩顿-斯坦-戈塞特律师行的律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm an attorney with Payton, Stein, and Gossett.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.37,0:35:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们拘留了一名联调局探员  汉娜·威尔士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have an FBI agent in custody -- Hannah Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.83,0:35:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的家人雇了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've been retained by her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.54,0:35:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要马上见到她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need to see her immediately, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.32,0:35:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}新信息\N未知号码
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.77,0:35:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}未知号码\N威尔士被释放  下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.70,0:35:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么事  -我是贝丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yeah. - It's Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.77,0:35:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不应该给我打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You shouldn't be calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.85,0:35:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盘问乔纳的联调局探员是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The FBI agent who questioned Joyner -- who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.05,0:35:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  乔纳没说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. Joyner didn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.25,0:35:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男的还是女的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, was it a man or a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.62,0:35:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女的  亚洲人  他好像说过  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A woman, Asian woman, I think he said. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.61,0:35:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  彼得  接电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Peter. Pick up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.17,0:35:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-您所拨打的用户...  -该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The subscriber you are trying to reach... - Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.59,0:36:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}保持安静
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.96,0:36:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  这两位是达姆沙克和帕尔默探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alvin, these are Agents Damashek and Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.04,0:36:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请抬起胳膊  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold your arms out, please, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.68,0:36:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们  我一会就回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, gentleman. Be with you in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.51,0:37:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's take a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.99,0:37:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对...  对不起  队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm -- I'm sorry, Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.24,0:37:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  不用道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no, no, don't be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.59,0:37:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.50,0:37:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太紧张了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get nervous, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.29,0:37:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被人发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone's gonna find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.91,0:37:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局手上有乘客名单\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The FBI -- they got this manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.81,0:37:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些形式主义的文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's paperwork, red tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.42,0:37:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道军方的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.73,0:37:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  队长  但事实是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know, Cap, but the truth --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.78,0:37:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实很久之前就被掩盖了  阿尔文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth got buried a long time ago, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.64,0:37:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但于我  于我的良心都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not for me, not in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.26,0:37:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是会看到他们的脸  我们做过的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I still see all their faces, what we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.16,0:37:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得振作起来  伙计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got to pull yourself together, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.89,0:37:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我死在那里  队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I'd died there, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.11,0:37:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别这样  -我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Oh, come on. - I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.29,0:37:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望自己没能回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wish I never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.70,0:37:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened that day was not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.52,0:37:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被出卖了  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were betrayed, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.06,0:37:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须自卫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We had to defend ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.10,0:38:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了拯救彼此我们不得不那样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did what we had to do to save each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.13,0:38:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于我的副总统身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This new office I'm in, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.77,0:38:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再这样来这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't be making visits like this anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.74,0:38:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要知道  我能信任你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so I need to know... can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.31,0:38:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《约翰福音》第八章第32节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}John 8:32.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.40,0:38:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  不  阿尔文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Alvin, no. Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.78,0:38:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你们必晓得真理"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"And you will know the truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.77,0:38:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很重要  这真的很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is important. This is so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.67,0:38:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-"真理必叫你们得以自由"  -你不懂多重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- "And the truth will set you free." - You don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.79,0:38:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是圣经  不是政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how important. That's the Bible. It's not the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府对真理没有兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The government's not interested in truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.86,0:38:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府才是撒谎的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the government that lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.88,0:38:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我们送进屠杀场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They sent us into a slaughterhouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.15,0:38:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后掩盖了事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then they covered it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.85,0:38:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们利用我们  那我们就利用他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They used us, so we used them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.26,0:38:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  你说了谎  我们都说了谎  阿尔文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, you lied. We all did, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.25,0:38:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对国会说谎  为了保护部队  保护你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I lied to Congress to protect the unit, to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.72,0:38:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要对得起...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got to live up to your end...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.96,0:38:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-够了  上吧  -我这样做并保护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's it. Go. - of the bargain and protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.27,0:38:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为如果你失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause if you fail to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.74,0:38:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不仅会毁掉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're not only gonna destroy us --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.23,0:38:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局  不许动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}FBI! Freeze! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.22,0:38:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克利什副总统  我以对美国国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Vice President MacLeish, I'm arresting you for perjury
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.02,0:38:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作伪证罪逮捕你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in front of the United States Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.17,0:38:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.38,0:39:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-现在  -快跑  队长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Now. - Run, Cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.08,0:39:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  目标在180米外\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's go. Target is 200 yards out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.30,0:39:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一发会打中的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The next one counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.78,0:39:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会对我开枪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not gonna shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.24,0:39:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手放在头上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.08,0:39:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么证据都没有  威尔士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got nothing, Wells.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.96,0:39:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.25,0:39:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.88,0:39:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是美国副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the vice president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.73,0:39:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是个警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're just a cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.94,0:39:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.28,0:40:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.92,0:40:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别操劳过度了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.39,0:40:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
